title: Please Vote For ACC Winner
summary:
Key ideas
- There are eight adversarial collaborations that have now been posted.
- Readers can vote for their favorite collaboration.
- There are cash prizes for first and second place winners.

Key learnings
- The author is not putting his finger on the scale this time in deciding the winner.
- The first place winner will receive $2000 and the second place winner will receive $500.
- Participants, readers, and voters are thanked for their involvement in the collaborations.

Key questions
- None mentioned in this portion of the post.
